In Emacs, folding can be achieved throught ''Outline mode'' (used by Org-mode, for example) or ''HideShow''.
http://www.emacswiki.org/HideShow

The keybinding for me (set in .emacs) is :

* `C-c h` for `hs-hide-block`
* `C-c s` for `hs-show-block`
* `C-c S` for `hs-show-all`
* `C-c H` for `hs-hide-all`